表格注塑产品信息表的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('ItemMstr')
and type = 'U')
drop table ItemMstr
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: ItemMstr */
/*==============================================================*/
create table ItemMstr (
ID int identity(1,1),
Item_Code varchar(20) not null,
ProductRemark varchar(200) null,
MouldCode varchar(20) not null,
ModeDesc varchar(200) null,
Mould_SpecialFittingsNo varchar(20) null,
InsertsDesc varchar(200) null,
PackageNum integer not null,
Item_Weight decimal(18, 2) not null,
Item_ActualGrossWgt decimal(18, 2) null,
Item_WaterGapScale decimal(18, 4) not null,
Item_Color varchar(50) null,
CustomerName varchar(100) null,
MaterialCode varchar(20) null,
MaterialDesc varchar(20) null,
PowderCode varchar(20) null,
AuxiliaryMaterialNo varchar(20) null,
AuxiliaryMaterialNum decimal(4, 2) null,
OutsideAssociation char(1) null,
MachineAssembly char(1) null,
ProdPhoto image null,
VerNo varchar(20) not null,
Creater varchar(20) not null,
CreateDate datetime not null,
ModiHistoryContent varchar(500) null,
Remark varchar(400) null,
StandEmployee varchar(20) null,
Processes varchar(20) null,
constraint PK_ITEMMSTR primary key (Item_Code)
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
